      "value": "A ceiling-fresco-style Baroque painting of plump winged cherubs floating among golden clouds — except they are all doing a high-energy 1980s aerobics workout. The chubby cherubs wear neon spandex leotards, sweatbands, and leg warmers over their tiny wings, frozen mid-jumping-jack and lunge with strained joyful expressions. One cherub leads from the front on a marble step, gesturing energetically; another fumbles a tiny dumbbell; a boombox carved from gilded marble sits on a cloud blasting music lines drawn as little gold notes. Trumpeting angels in the corners blow whistles instead of horns. Soft heavenly light streams from above in golden god-rays, illuminating rosy skin and pastel spandex, billowing fabric and clouds. Painted in the lush, luminous style of Tiepolo with theatrical foreshortening, but the costume colors are electric hot-pink, lime, and cyan. Rendered with the warm, fine-grain look of Kodak Ektachrome E100. Divine, ridiculous, gloriously sincere."
